{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"c7457a20-297a-4243-84bf-fa14406c56e4","agentId":"ab886da16184dbb41","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"You are implementing Task 4 for the `project-reader` Claude Code plugin. Your job: create ONE file and commit it.\n\n## Scene\n\nThis plugin is a Claude Code plugin (stored at `~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/`). You are creating `agents/structure-explorer.md` — a Claude Code agent that performs deep directory scanning and generates the project module map.\n\n## Task 4: structure-explorer agent\n\n**File to create:**\n- `~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/agents/structure-explorer.md`\n\n## Exact content to write\n\n```bash\ncat > ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/agents/structure-explorer.md << 'EOF'\n---\nname: structure-explorer\ndescription: 扫描项目目录树，结合 entry-finder 和语言特化 skill，生成完整模块地图（PROJECT_MAP.md）并更新 INDEX.md。由 /read 命令触发调用。\ntools: Glob, Grep, Read, Write, Bash\nmodel: sonnet\n---\n\n# Structure Explorer Agent\n\n你是项目结构分析专家。任务：深度扫描当前项目，生成模块地图，写入持久化缓存。\n\n## 输入\n\n从调用方接收：\n- `project_key`：`<project-name>-<hash8>` 格式的缓存键\n- `lang_result`：project-detector 输出的 JSON\n- `force`：是否强制重新分析（默认 false）\n\n## 执行流程\n\n### Phase 1: 目录树扫描\n\n使用 Glob 和 Bash（执行 `find` 或 `ls`）扫描项目根目录。\n\n**跳过以下目录（不进入内部分析）：**\n- `.git/`、`node_modules/`、`build/`、`DerivedData/`\n- `Pods/`（仅记录存在性）、`__pycache__/`、`.gradle/`、`.build/`\n\n生成两层结构：\n1. 顶层目录列表（含简要职责推断）\n2. 每个顶层目录的直接子项列表\n\n### Phase 2: 模块职责推断\n\n根据目录/文件命名规律推断职责：\n\n**iOS 命名规律：**\n- `Feature*/`、`Modules/` → 功能模块层\n- `Services/`、`*Service` → 服务层\n- `ViewModels/`、`*ViewModel` → ViewModel 层\n- `Coordinators/`、`*Coordinator` → 导航协调层\n- `Utils/`、`Helpers/` → 工具层\n- `Resources/`、`Assets.xcassets` → 资源层\n- `Tests/`、`*Tests/` → 测试层\n\n**通用规律：**\n- `src/`、`lib/`、`include/` → 核心源码\n- `docs/` → 文档\n- `scripts/`、`tools/` → 工具脚本\n- `config/`、`*.yaml`、`*.toml` → 配置\n\n### Phase 3: 入口文件标注\n\n基于 `lang_result` 中的 `key_files`，在模块地图中标注：\n- 🚀 App 入口（AppDelegate/SceneDelegate/@main）\n- 🔗 跨语言桥接（.mm 文件、Bridging Header）\n- 📦 依赖声明（Podfile、Package.swift、CMakeLists.txt）\n- 🧩 git submodule（来自 lang_result.submodules）\n\n### Phase 4: 写入 PROJECT_MAP.md\n\n写入路径：`~/.claude/analyses/<project_key>/PROJECT_MAP.md`\n\n格式参考 `templates/project-map.md` 模板（在 Task 8 中创建，执行时应已就位）。\n\n### Phase 5: 更新 INDEX.md\n\n更新 `~/.claude/analyses/<project_key>/INDEX.md`：\n- 将分析状态从「轻量扫描」更新为「完整分析」\n- 更新最后分析时间\n- 添加模块列表摘要（最多 10 个主要模块）\n\n## 输出\n\n分析完成后，向用户输出摘要（不超过 20 行）：\n1. 检测到的语言组合\n2. 主要模块列表（每行一个，含职责说明）\n3. 入口文件路径\n4. 关键依赖清单\n5. 分析结果保存路径\n\n## 约束\n\n- 不修改目标项目任何文件\n- 只写入 `~/.claude/analyses/` 目录\n- 单个目录扫描深度不超过 4 层\nEOF\n```\n\n## Verification\n\n```bash\nhead -8 ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/agents/structure-explorer.md\n```\n\nExpected: frontmatter with name/description/tools/model, tools field must be `Glob, Grep, Read, Write, Bash` (NOT LS).\n\n## Commit\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader\ngit add agents/structure-explorer.md\ngit commit -m \"feat: add structure-explorer agent for full project scan\"\n```\n\n## Status to Report\n\nReport **DONE** or **BLOCKED**. Include the `head -8` output."},"uuid":"f9ee897f-5198-4108-aa60-1c20a766e273","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:52:54.782Z","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/xpeng/Desktop/AiStudy/claude-learn/plugin-dev","sessionId":"95b3d4f4-8123-4885-9752-f1e600f4a1f6","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"frolicking-honking-lake"}
